<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          MORFOLOGIA
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">Le esclamazioni</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        92
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 font-semibold">
      Le esclamazioni (o interiezioni) esprimono uno stato d'animo o una sensazione improvvisa (sorpresa, gioia, dolore, noia…).
      Sono seguite dal punto esclamativo o dai punti di sospensione.
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Le <strong class="text-blue-600">esclamazioni proprie</strong> sono parole che si usano solo come esclamazioni: Ahi! Oh! Ohi! Ahia! Uffa! Boh! Suvvia! Ahimè!...</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Le <strong class="text-green-600">esclamazioni improprie</strong> sono aggettivi, nomi, gruppi di parole usati come esclamazioni: Bene!, Aiuto!, Bravo!, Accipicchia!, Forza!, Meno male!, Mamma mia!...</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold mr-2">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Collega ogni esclamazione all'emozione corrispondente.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Esclamazioni -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-yellow-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-3">Esclamazioni</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Uffa!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Evviva!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Ahimè!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Ahi!</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2 font-semibold">Boh!</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Emozioni -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border-2 border-green-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-green-700 mb-3">Emozioni</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>abbattimento</em> → Ahimè!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>noia</em> → Uffa!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>gioia</em> → Evviva!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>incertezza</em> → Boh!</div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2"><em>dolore</em> → Ahi!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="word-highlighter" data-word-highlighter-multi-color-value="true">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      <span>Sottolinea <span class="text-yellow-600">esclamazioni proprie<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-yellow-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="yellow" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span> e <span class="text-blue-600">esclamazioni improprie<span class="inline-block w-6 h-6 bg-blue-300 rounded ml-1 align-middle cursor-pointer transition transform hover:scale-110" data-word-highlighter-target="colorBox" data-color="blue" data-action="click->word-highlighter#selectColor"></span></span>.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg cursor-pointer">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Ah</span>, non dire bugie!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Accipicchia</span>, che capitombolo!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Forza</span>! Ancora un po' e siamo arrivati.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Che bel lavoro: <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">brava</span>!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Mamma mia</span>, che spavento ho preso!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Ehi</span>, mi ascolti o parlo al vento?</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="blue">Povero me</span>, sono proprio nei guai!</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• <span class="transition" data-word-highlighter-target="word" data-action="click->word-highlighter#toggleHighlight" data-correct="yellow">Uh</span>, come sei sfortunato!</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
      Scrivi una frase per ciascuna delle seguenti esclamazioni.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-base md:text-lg mb-4">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        Bene!
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        Zitto!
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        Basta!
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        Ohi ohi!
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• </span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-full md:w-4/5" placeholder=".....................................................................">
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• </span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-full md:w-4/5" placeholder=".....................................................................">
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• </span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-full md:w-4/5" placeholder=".....................................................................">
      </div>
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• </span>
        <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-green-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-full md:w-4/5" placeholder=".....................................................................">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
